0
\end{array}\right),
\]

\end_inset

 and correspondingly for 
\begin_inset Formula $\Omega_{6,4}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\begin{array}{c}
1\\
-1\\
0\\
0
\end{array}\right)\mapsto\left(\begin{array}{c}
